MOVE IN READY AND A GREAT LOCATION - A MUST SEE TO BELIEVE.  WONDERFUL FIREPLACE IN THE LIVINGROOM TO KEEP THE HOUSE COZY IN THE FALL;  TILE AND LAMINATE FLOORING TO KEEP COOL IN THE SUMMER HEAT.  WONDERFUL KITCHEN FOR COOKING MEALS FOR FAMILY GATHERINGS OR ENTERTAINING FRIENDS ON THE COVERED BACK PORCH; THE REFRIGERATOR STAYS WITH THE HOUSE !  WOW !  ROOMY MASTERBEDROOM WITH COMFORTABLE ADDITIONAL BEDROOMS, CEILING FANS WITH INTERIOR PLANTATION SHUTTERS. TASTEFULLY PAINTED INTERIOR, LARGE FENCED YARD WITH TWO SHEDS AND A PEACEFUL NEIGHBORHOOD. GARAGE DOOR BRAND NEW.

HOUSE AVAILABLE FOR SHOWINGS....IGNORE BROKER BAY AND SHOWING TIME-Not sure what's up with that.
